Package: Visualizr
Type: Package
Title: R Package To Visualize And Explore Raw Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "John Wood <jmw.home@gmail.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Trenton Pulsipher <trenton.pulsipher@henryschein.com> [aut]"
  ))
Maintainer: John Wood <jmw.home@gmail.com>
Description: Visualizr provides an exaustive set of useful statistics and plots
    on new data to help streamline EDA. The primary goal of the package is to 
    provide better understanding of what variables and data are important in a
    shorter amount of time. 
